      "date": "2016-01-29 13:31:57.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nTests uploaded by Shadow Autotest2 from shadow-22vm1 for review-dne-part-1 received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/7fc25060-c68c-11e5-8d9f-5254006e85c2). Ran 7 tests.  No failures.",
